        <!-- LEGEND -->
        <mxCell id="80" value="&lt;b&gt;Business Value&lt;/b&gt; — 4 actionable segments from 500K+ transactions enable personalised marketing: win-back campaigns for At-Risk, loyalty rewards for Champions, onboarding sequences for Promising customers&#xa;&lt;b&gt;SA/SE Angle&lt;/b&gt; — Demonstrates data-to-insight pipeline design, model selection rigour (Silhouette + elbow), and translating ML outputs into business recommendations (exactly what pre-sales SEs do in POC readouts)&#xa;&lt;b&gt;Scalability&lt;/b&gt; — Pipeline design maps directly onto AWS: S3 + AWS Glue for ETL, SageMaker Processing for feature engineering + training, QuickSight for cluster dashboards" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=#8C4FFF;fillColor=#F4ECFF;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=1;fontSize=11;spacingLeft=10;spacingRight=10;" vertex="1" parent="1">
